  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967170/extras/6d2260f333f3d224f741b3e369ee7cd9.avif?t=1643382054\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>Get the hottest drum kits with Drum Simulator! Download this application and start jamming! Learn to play drums or repeat your parts at any moment. Download additional drum presets for different rock styles and enjoy playing with high quality sounds!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967170/extras/b66a0e72c0f612d6282b3d7ebe089484.avif?t=1643382054\" width=600 height=294 /></span><br><br>No hedge to become a rock drummer!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose between different drum kits;<br></li><li>Amazing music genres;<br></li><li>Various game modes.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967170/extras/bba83bdb5311ea9a359916d76b9fa298.avif?t=1643382054\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 professionally recorded sound packs;<br></li><li>Record your own drum beats and play them back;<br></li><li>Complete challenges in game mode.</li></ul><br>Take your drum skills to the highest level with Drum Simulator!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967170/extras/ee9ff84b8fc77eec0f46f0999f5fd771.webp?t=1643382054\" width=600 height=55 /></span>",
